# unittestingangularjs

AngularJS Unit Test
Karma
Jasmine
PhantomJS

Install AngularJS Unit Test

* nodejs
* bower (using npm)

- npm init
- npm install bower --save-dev (install bower)
> app folder to install AngularJS
- bower init -> (config some default)
- bower install angular --save
* set up karma, jasmine, phantomjs (root)
- npm install karma-cli phantomjs –g
- karma --version (check karma version)
- phantomjs --version (check phantomjs version)
- npm install karma jasmine --save-dev
       cd app
> bower install angular-mocks --save-dev

cd js/test
> karma init (config karma)
config list of file karma.conf.js
> karma start karma.conf.js


